Titolo: Buzz!: The Sports Quiz

Anno: 2006

Descrizione: Buzz!: The Sports Quiz for the PlayStation 2, is the third game in the Buzz! series and was developed by Kuju Entertainment. Like the previous two games in the series (Buzz!: The Music Quiz, Buzz!: The BIG Quiz), it was released for the PlayStation 2 exclusively in Europe. Players answer questions  asked by the Quizmaster (Buzz) using their Buzz! buzzers.

Genere: Party 

Valutazione: N/A
